item.title: LS Episode 500: What the Helly?! (feat. Rob49)
item.description:
Rob49 joins Lip Service for a wild, unfiltered conversation about loyalty, privacy, fame, and his viral "What the Helly" movement. He opens up about celebrating success, relationships, role play, working with Justin Bieber, and why he values real support over clout. Plus, Rob shares stories from his come-up in New Orleans, plans for his festival, and hilarious drunk confessions from the podcast.
